//Home page// Battleship Settings Welcome to BATTLESHIP! Start Game By: Coco and Claudia
//Instruction page// Instructions: Welcome to Battleship! Press the Start Game button on the menu page to begin a game. Follow the prompts to place your ship and attack the opponent. There is a two length Destroyer, a three length Submarine, a three length Cruiser, and a four length Battleship. Make sure not to overlap your ships! Upon attack, the square chosen will turn black if the attack was unsuccessful, and red if an enemy ship has been hit. Sink all the enemy ships before they sink yours to win! Press the back button to go back to the menu and start a game. Back to Menu
